BuildRequires:	libX11-devel, libSM-devel, libXi-devel, libXmu-devel
BuildRequires:	SDL2-devel, SDL2_image-devel, openal-soft-devel, freealut-devel
BuildRequires:	mesa-libGLU-devel, mesa-libGL-devel, libICE-devel
